snippet.title: Shantae and the Pirate's Curse Official Trailer
snippet.description: When Sequin Land falls under a curse, Shantae must join forces with her arch nemesis Risky Boots to battle unimaginable evil! The third game in the Shantae pixel series, only for Nintendo 3DS.
